h1 Control stuff by throwing shapes

Understand common poses:
shh, single finger raised to lips, either hand
stop, hand raised palm forward, either hand
kill, single finger drawn across throat, either hand
select or point, single finger forward, arm raised, either hand
etc

context implied by timing and position (irrespective of camera location):
to pause Netflix perform stop whilst facing the TV
to turn off a light, point at it, then perform kill
to mute music, perform ssh whilst facing music source
